Glad to meet with USG Voronkov.

Multilateral cooperation is essential to effectively counter terrorism, which is a common enemy of humanity.

🇨🇳 supports UN in playing a central coordinating role in global CT efforts, and will continue to work with @UN_OCT to #CounterTerrorism.
